debug.Description: turn on debugging features of mediawiki

name.Description: The name, or Title of the Wiki

server_address.Description: The server url to set "$wgServer". Useful for reverse proxies

use_suffix.Description: If we should put '/mediawiki' suffix on the url

charm-metadata.Name: mediawiki
charm-metadata.Description:
MediaWiki is a wiki engine (a program for creating a collaboratively
edited website). It is designed to handle heavy websites containing
library-like document collections, and supports user uploads of
images/sounds, multilingual content, TOC autogeneration, ISBN links,
etc.

bzr-revisions.message: [dannf] Restrict personal namespace PPA to precise
[lazypower] Refactors out phantomjs/selenium - uses requests and title validation.
[hackedbellini] Allow to remove the "/mediawiki" suffix and to change the wgServer config
[lazypower] Renamed setup to conform to charm add tests command, validated required dependencies via vagrant issued juju test on clean env

Testing

Adds integration tests for unit deploy, db relationship with mysql, and cache relationship with memcached
